window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>She isn’t supposed to be mine.</i></b><br> <br> I am the illegitimate son. Unwanted. Hated. The jealous, possessive villain who once wore the mask of a hero.<br> <br> Ophelia Hart is the girl next door.<br> <br> Growing up, I rescued her countless times from my idiot half-brother.<br> <br> Now, the rivalry between him and me has changed. The stakes are higher. And Ophelia is in danger.<br> <br> But I’ll be damned if I let him touch her.<br> <br> She no longer thinks me the hero of her story, though.<br> <br> She’ll fight me.<br> <br> I’ll fight for her.<br> <br> But there comes a time in every man’s life where he must take what he wants.<br> <br> That time is now.<br> <br> Because there is no way in hell I will let my half-brother have her.</p>"; 
